d-canine-1.jpg\"}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":10,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/cornelius-pet-care-llc\",\"name\":\"Cornelius Pet Care LLC\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/cornelius-pet-care-llc\",\"description\":\"Among Huntersville's top-rated facilities, Cornelius Pet Care LLC excels in year-round care. This facility features spacious exercise zones, knowledgeable animal handlers, offering pet care. Their...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Huntersville\",\"addressRegion\":\"NC\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"image\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/cornelius-pet-care-llc/cornelius-pet-care-llc-1.jpg\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where can I hike with my dog in Huntersville?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Latta Nature Preserve is the premier destination, offering miles of hiking trails along Mountain Island Lake. It is a nature lover’s paradise.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is there a dog park in Huntersville?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, Rosedale Nature Park features a dedicated dog park. Additionally, the nearby Ramsey Creek Park in Cornelius is a short drive and offers lake access.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is Birkdale Village dog-friendly?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Very. Birkdale Village is an open-air shopping center where many stores welcome dogs, and water bowls are commonly found outside shops.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can dogs swim in Lake Norman?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"At Ramsey Creek Park (nearby), there is a dog park with water access. However, generally, dogs should be kept on leash near the water in public parks unless designated otherwise.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Parks Directory\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Huntersville\"}]}</script><header class=\"header header-visible  header-light\"><div class=\"header-container\"><div class=\"header-left\"><a class=\"logo\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Indoor Dog Park logo\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;object-fit:contain;height:auto\" src=\"/images/logo/logo.png\"/></a></div><div class=\"header-center\"><nav class=\"header-nav\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Discover <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a></div></div><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Locations <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-francisco\">San Francisco</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/los-angeles\">Los Angeles</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-diego\">San Diego</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/new-york\">New York</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/seattle\">Seattle</a></div></div><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/abou