ature lover’s paradise.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is there a dog park in Huntersville?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, Rosedale Nature Park features a dedicated dog park. Additionally, the nearby Ramsey Creek Park in Cornelius is a short drive and offers lake access.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is Birkdale Village dog-friendly?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Very. Birkdale Village is an open-air shopping center where many stores welcome dogs, and water bowls are commonly found outside shops.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can dogs swim in Lake Norman?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"At Ramsey Creek Park (nearby), there is a dog park with water access. However, generally, dogs should be kept on leash near the water in public parks unless designated otherwise.\"}}]}26:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2e\"}}]\n27:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Huntersville\\\"}]}\"}}]\n28:[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n29:[\"$\",\"$L2f\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"title\":\"Map & Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"planning-essentials\",\"title\":\"Planning Essentials\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"expert-tips\",\"title\":\"Expert Advice\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-directory\",\"title\":\"Full Directory\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"owner-cta\",\"title\":\"Owner & Franchise\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"faq-section\",\"title\":\"FAQs\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"title\":\"More Resources\",\"level\":1}]}]\n2a:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Huntersville\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Lake Norman Life\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Huntersville Adventures\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-chip-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"hero-chip\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Nature Preserve\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"1\"}],\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"hero-chip\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Lake Access\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"Yes\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Nestled along Lake Norman, Huntersville offers the best of both worlds: rugged hiking at Latta Nature Preserve and refined patio dining at Birkdale Village.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Huntersville, North Carolina, offers a lifestyle defined by its proximity to Lake Norman, and for dog owners, this means unparalleled access to nature and water. The crown jewel is the \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://parkandrec.mecknc.gov/Places-to-Visit/Nature-Preserves-and-Nature-Centers/Latta-Nature-Preserve\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"Latta Nature Preserve\"}],null,\", a sprawling natural area that serves as the county’s largest nature preserve. Here, miles of hiking trails wind through hardwood forests and along the shoreline, offering a sensory feast for dogs. While swimming is restricted in many areas, the views and the quality of the hike make it a top destination for active owners.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Contrast this rugged beauty with Birkdale Village, an open-air shopping and dining destination that mimics a classic main street. It is the social heart of Huntersville and is famously dog-friendly. You will see countless residents walking their dogs past shop windows, stopping for water bowls left out by merchants, or lounging on restaurant patios. Rosedale Nature Park adds a dedicated off-leash facility to the mix, ensuring that whether you want a vigorous hike, a social shopping trip, or a game of fetch, Huntersville has a high-quality option \",[\"$\",\"$L12\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/training-facilities\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"ready for you\"}],null,\".\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Latta Nature Preserve\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Latta Nature Preserve\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Birkdale Village\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Birkdale Village\"]}],\"$L31\"]}]]}],\"$L32\"]}]}],\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\",\"$L37\",\"$L38\",\"$undefined\",\"$L39\",\"$L3a\",\"$L3b\",\"$L3c\",\"$L3d\"]}]\n2b:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-new\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-grid\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-column\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h4\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-heading\",\"children\":\"IndoorDogPark\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-links\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/about\",\"children\":\"About us\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"ch